Assignment 4 features

There are 3 viewing changes implemented:
- You can rotate the windows centered to the ant using keyboard arrows left and right (View Transformation)
- You can move the eyepoint just by moving the mouse in the window (View Transformation)
- You can zoom in the object by scrolling up and zoom out by scrolling down (Projection Transformation)

You can select joints to spin. The active joint being spinned is red colored.
- To move to the next joint press N
- To rotate the joint use wasd
- The head is the only one that spins in two axis

Bonus implemented:
- You can make the ant walk by pressing G on your keyboard
